name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Github File History By Commits - View File

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When viewing history for a single file, adds a new button with a link to view the file at the commit point in the history.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When viewing history for a single file, adds a new button with a link to view the file at the commit point in the history.

Document SVG icon is from: https://heroicons.dev/.

Run the code only if the page is "History for" (https://github.com/*/*/commits/*`) pages with the breadcrumbs.
